            <p>The Department of Child & Adolescent Health, at ESIC Medical College Hospital, is a state-of-the-art
            facility which deals with comprehensive care and management of health problems in children and adolescents.
            Our team of experienced paediatricians, neonatologists, paediatric intensive care doctors and neonatal
            nurses work 24x7 while adhering to evidence-based treatment guidelines approached from multiple
            disciplines. We also offer critical care with a dedicated NICU for children who require intensive care
            monitoring, immunization services for ESIC dependant beneficiaries over and above conducting regular CMEs,
            Workshops and training classes for UG students of medical and nursing education.</p>

            <p>This department has expertise in Paediatric, Neonatal Critical Care and support staff who work round the
            clock.</p>

            <p>Facilities available are</p>

            <p>1.Paediatric snd neonatal intensive care services<br>
            2.Outpatient Consultation<br>
            3.Well baby and immunisation services<br>
            4.Follow-up of the inpatients with chronic illness<br>
            5.Services of Paediatric Phlebotomist<br>
            6.Paediatric Surgery, with a multi-disciplinary approach<br>
            7.Superspecialty services for Paediatric endocrinology, ophthalmology ( mostly ROP and Type l Diabetes) and
            Asthma</p>
